<p>Here are the details of your order received on <%= order.completed_at.strftime("%B %d %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.</p>
<p>Your order number is <strong class="pink"><%= order.number %></strong> Please keep it for reference if you speak to a customer service representative.</p>

<% if order.store.code == "nwb" %>
  <p>
    Click on the link below to login to your account and to check your order status.<br>
    <a href="https://www.naturalwellbeing.com/orders/<%= order.number %>">https://www.naturalwellbeing.com/orders/<%= order.number %></a>
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
    Click on the link below to login to your account and to check your order status.<br/>
    <a href="https://www.petwellbeing.com/orders/<%= order.number %>">https://www.petwellbeing.com/orders/<%= order.number %></a>
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>Your <%= order.store.name %> order includes the following item(s):</p>
<%= render "order_details_html", :order => order %>